item.description:
11th Annual Braintree Athletic Association Thanksgiving Day 5K Road Race And Walk

Don't feel guilty when you reach for that 2nd piece of pie! Toss the turkey in the oven and head to BSH to join us for a little exercise for spending the day with family and friends.

This is a LARGE event. We will meet in the Cafeteria of the HS. I will wear a Red Sox fleece with a VERY large symbol of the Sox in front. (see the picture I posted for this event to look for me!)
*I post this event for 7am to allow time to pick up bib #'s, stretch and meet.

Thursday, November 25, 2010
8:00 AM Start (7:45 AM Walkers)
A Great Community Event

Start and End at BHS
Registration 7:00 AM, BHS Cafeteria

$17 registration before November 19th or $20 day of the race
Long Sleeve Tee Shirts
*GUARANTEED TO THE 1st 200 REGISTERED RUNNERS ONLY*
Prize for top finishers in each age category

Checks Made Payable to: BHS Athletic Association
Mail to: Braintree High School, c/o Mike Denise, 128 Town Street, Braintree, MA 02184

***MAIL IN REGISTRATION ONLY, NO ONLINE AVAILABLE***
REGISTRATION FORMS AVAILABLE AT THIS LINK:

http://www.gpvillage....
item.how_to_find_us: I will be wearing the same Sox fleece in the picture. Look for me in the BHS Cafeteria
